info.author: Sarwat Khan
info.description:
Reads and writes CoreFoundation XML property lists (.plist files) using an 
interface similar to Cocoa's NSPropertyListSerialization.

Includes Cocoa-style Data and Date (datetime) classes. The Date class includes 
an ISO8601 string parser and implements NSDate reference-date methods.
info.name: plistservices
info.summary: CoreFoundation Property List (.plist) and ISO 8601 date string parser
info.html_description:
Reads and writes CoreFoundation XML property lists (.plist files) using an interface similar to Cocoa’s NSPropertyListSerialization.

Includes Cocoa-style Data and Date (datetime) classes. The Date class includes an ISO8601 string parser and implements NSDate reference-date methods.
